  <refsect1>
     <title>Description</title>
     <para>The <link linkend="class-ossoabookalphabar">
        <classname>abook.AlphaBar</classname></link>
        is a bar of locale-specific shortcuts to ranges
        of alphanumeric characters. When a shortcut is
        activated, the cursor of the associated
        <link linkend="class-ossoabooktreeview">
        <classname>abook.TreeView</classname></link> will
        be moved to the first row starting with one of the
        characters from the range.</para>

        <para>There are two ways to use an
        <link linkend="class-ossoabookalphabar">
        <classname>abook.AlphaBar</classname></link>. The first
        one is to merge it into a
        <link linkend="class-gtkuimanager">
        <classname>gtk.UIManager</classname></link> using
        <link linkend="method-ossoabookalphabar--merge">
        <methodname>abook.AlphaBar.merge()</methodname></link>.
        The second one is to create an independent array of buttons using
        <link linkend="method-ossoabookalphabar--create-button-row">
        <methodname>abook.AlphaBar.create_button_row()</methodname></link>. </para>
  </refsect1>
